{"product_id":"vielo-organic-foot-balm-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Foot  Balm 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic foot balm, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry feet and cracked heels.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply to clean and dry skin and massage in well. Regular use helps to protect the skin from drying out.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/Stearate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Betaine*, Aqua*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Tocopherol*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Limonene**\/***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (88,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oil\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901104427335,"sku":null,"price":20.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-foot-balm-50ml-911694.jpg?v=1739897171","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/vielo-organic-foot-balm-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}